2000-10-28  Tor Lillqvist  <tml@iki.fi>

	* makefile.{mingw,msc}.in: Make glib-genmarshal.exe.

	* glib-genmarshal.c: Conditionalise include of unistd.h.
	Include <io.h> on Win32.

